        " اَلصَّادِقُ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ : \"مَنِ اِكْتَحَلَ بِمِيلٍ مِنْ مُسْكِرٍ كَحَلَهُ اَللَّهُ بِمِيلٍ مِنْ نَارٍ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.4947 - Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) said:\n\"Whoever applies kohl with a stick dipped in an intoxicant, Allah will apply a stick of fire to his eyes.\""
        ]
